{"tid":114222,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"求救（周身痕）","createTime":"2017-02-09T15:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T16:27:55.000Z","uid":11007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"094f3af09e0414312a5de7c7bf7dcfbc08829860","tid":114222,"uid":11007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:03:27.000Z","msg":"下晝開始成身都痕 但又唔係比蚊針 r左陣開始即發現個身有紅點 到左而家 手 腳都有好多風book 手踭位最嚴重 大小不一0既風book 生哂係度 本來以為係乾燥 諗著沖完涼茶cream會無事 點知都係唔得 而家仲係好痕 有無人知究竟咩原因會搞到咁"},{"pid":"84a59c6760811fafaa3bf266b6ae1db1a34d3a4f","tid":114222,"uid":49298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:04:11.000Z","msg":"生性病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e72362a4750ab394ed5db6c9225742a7766e95","tid":114222,"uid":26937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:07:56.000Z","msg":"睇次醫生check次先<br />\n我早排痕左兩個月<br />\n沖涼茶豬油膏就好返了<br />\n真係痕到夜晚扎醒<br />\n好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a598db008f45006fa23885df08b4c24b88d3ad7","tid":114222,"uid":11007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:10:25.000Z","msg":"仲以為係乾燥 猛咁茶cream 點知都仲係痕 紅風book又唔散 痕到想死  聽日都唔散就睇醫生了"},{"pid":"834ecf297826edde16f978307d99da474df3529d","tid":114222,"uid":60751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:12:03.000Z","msg":"係唔係風癩呀？"},{"pid":"c5361232a72002879c72c9218dcdeeaae5fbf844","tid":114222,"uid":70484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"唔好搽cream 你唔知咩事仲搽可能仲痕<br />\n食粒敏感藥快啲瞓 <br />\n聽日再無好轉先睇醫生<br />\n沖涼唔好用熱水 儘量用偏凍水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 皮膚敏感人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27774501df9e5ba8fd3b72366d1c324f159e042","tid":114222,"uid":2195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:48:25.000Z","msg":"濕疹？"},{"pid":"6034eb5729e78b6943dcb1faee248e98c506ecf8","tid":114222,"uid":75874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:11:52.000Z","msg":"如果係風癱試下沖乾淨涼<br />\n將啲米酒倒落啲紙巾/綿花到撻住佢 撻到唔痕為止<br />\n同埋留意下自己食過乜野所以出風癱下次小心飲食"},{"pid":"69406d2570e28687b1303b9c15da4035341f4e2a","tid":114222,"uid":5286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:17:16.000Z","msg":"梳打沖涼"},{"pid":"90cc134909d0d6cf8a56c8ffe4966b8380a567f1","tid":114222,"uid":5286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:19:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梳打沖涼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry ，應該咁講<br />\n<br />\n花椒八角煲水，或者梳打開水。攞嚟抺身"},{"pid":"a1def6d3d3e2974335c7a3e3110b00dcd3229a44","tid":114222,"uid":13752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:20:06.000Z","msg":"我前幾日開始都係咁<br />\n全身都好痕 有好多紅點 但唔係濕疹都唔係風癩<br />\n我都諗住聽日睇醫生... 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37247a15c446e8d828921fdd77fb2c977ef811af","tid":114222,"uid":13752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:21:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我前幾日開始都係咁<br />\n全身都好痕 有好多紅點 但唔係濕疹都唔係風癩<br />\n我都諗住聽日睇醫生... 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有試過搽椰子油 以為乾燥但係無用 都係好痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823860b22fc6a87e6316966faa258177c6cd04b1","tid":114222,"uid":82960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:26:00.000Z","msg":"我覺得似風癩,試過,好似你咁,兩次都係冬天發作."},{"pid":"b0180608a22288cf64e3d90a86068cf4c641047c","tid":114222,"uid":13752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:27:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得似風癩,試過,好似你咁,兩次都係冬天發作.</blockquote><br />\n我試過有風癩 風癩唔係咁嘅<br />\n我全身係啲小紅點好似比蚊咬但唔係<br />\n都唔會有蚤 因為我同人同床訓 另一個人無事"}]}